# Autonomous Execution Framework

See [AUTONOMOUS_EXECUTION_FRAMEWORK.md](../../AUTONOMOUS_EXECUTION_FRAMEWORK.md).

## Rules

1. Aipify is never an uncontrolled agent — observe, suggest, prepare, execute only inside approved limits.
2. Package gate: `business` and `enterprise` only; Starter/Growth see upgrade notice.
3. Forbidden action types are blocked by `validate_aipify_action_safety()` — no refunds, admin permission changes, etc.
4. Autonomous level and execution rules require Enterprise plan.
5. Every action lifecycle event is logged in `aipify_action_logs` — no silent execution.
6. Route: `/app/action-center` (spec `/admin/action-center`); APIs at `/api/aipify/*`.
7. i18n: `customerApp.actionCenter.*`, `platform.aef.*` in en/no/sv/da.

